    "description": "Little Bo Peep has lost her sheep, and now she's out for revenge! Play as Bo Peep in a single-player 3D action-RPG where she's overwhelmed with grief and goes on an adventure through Pastoria. Command a variety of sheep flocks for you to fight your way through hordes of fairy-tale creatures on a brutal revenge quest for the sake of all sheep and animals. Use your necromancy powers taught to you by your old mentor, Baba Yaga - It must be because of all of her evil ways that all of your sheep were killed! Battle, train and learn new abilities to gain an advantage on the big trolls, spitting flowers or kamikaze frogs! Earn their souls to upgrade your abilities and unlock new ways of fighting to fit your own playstyle, such as riding your sheep into battle! You must discover the unique aspects of the land, including solving puzzles, platforming or discovering the long lost skulls. Find Baba Yaga and let her know how much those sheep meant to you, though she might be more prepared than you think!<br><br>Construct your sheep into various shapes to help you on your quest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/f59b5ff30fccb681133d6a7e19577b02.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/f59b5ff30fccb681133d6a7e19577b02.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/f59b5ff30fccb681133d6a7e19577b02.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lift yourself to the sky by stacking sheep on top of one another.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/4589842ad64020d0b7783999ac20171c.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/4589842ad64020d0b7783999ac20171c.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/4589842ad64020d0b7783999ac20171c.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Crash through walls with your Rams to solve puzzles and unlock cool secrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/614ba83f3b1aa34808b40cad42b6d436.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/614ba83f3b1aa34808b40cad42b6d436.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/614ba83f3b1aa34808b40cad42b6d436.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Cast a breeze of Fluffy Sheep into a vortex to overwhelm your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/eb8737e963a78437e9d072f36cbb7474.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/eb8737e963a78437e9d072f36cbb7474.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/eb8737e963a78437e9d072f36cbb7474.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Launch your sheep at your enemies from a distance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/1f63b72e520b85dad88036ac92994394.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/1f63b72e520b85dad88036ac92994394.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/1f63b72e520b85dad88036ac92994394.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect Souls from your enemies to spend on upgrades for your abilities, or even unlock new ones!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/827689e2b3c4399b81a7cb1c55cdbb61.poster.avif?t=1704268843\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/827689e2b3c4399b81a7cb1c55cdbb61.webm?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315940/extras/827689e2b3c4399b81a7cb1c55cdbb61.mp4?t=1704268843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
